Akagera ni imwe muri pariki nasiyonali z'igihugu cy'u Rwanda, Iyi pariki iri ku buso bwa kilometero kare 1122<ref>https://www.rba.co.rw/post/Pariki-yIgihugu-yAkagera-iza-ku-isonga-mu-zisurwa-cyane-mu-Rwanda</ref>. Ikora ku turere twa Kayonza, [[Akarere ka Nyagatare|Nyagatare]] na [[Akarere ka Gatsibo|Gatsibo]] mu burasirazuba bw’u [[Rwanda|Rwanda.]] Ni imwe muri pariki 3 z'igihugu zisurwa cyane na ba mukerarugendo benshi, ikaba ari na yo nini.

Pariki y’Akagera igizwe n’ibiyaga 10 birimo: ikiyaga cy'[[Hema|Ihema]] cyakuye izina ku Babiligi bahashinze amahema ubwo bashakishaga isoko ya [[Nili|Nil.]] Inyamaswa ugenda uzisanga ahantu bitewe n’impamvu eshatu: aho inyamaswa ibonera [[umutekano]], aho ikura ibyo [[kurya]] n’[[ubuhehere]] buharangwa ikenera.

Abasura pariki y’Akagera bavuga ko banezezwa n'ubwoko bw'inyamaswa buyibarizwamo cyane inyamaswa eshanu (5) nini z'inkazi  arizo: [[Inkura]], [[Intare]], [[Imbogo]], [[Inzovu]] n[[Ingwe|’Ingwe]].<ref>https://www.igihe.com/ubukerarugendo/pariki-n-amashyamba/article/sura-pariki-y-akagera-umenye-ibitangaje-ku-nkura-isatura-inzovu-mutware-n</ref>

Akagera gatuwe n'amoko y'[[Inyoni zo mu Rwanda|inyoni]] agera kuri 490<ref>https://www.visitrwanda.com/destinations/akagera-national-park/</ref>


'''<big>Amateka</big>'''

Parike ya Akagera yashinzwe mu 1934 na guverinoma y'Ububiligi,  igihe yigaruriraga u Rwanda. Parike yari ifite ibiro metero 2,500 mu bunini kandi yari izwiho ibinyabuzima bitandukanye.

Akagera pariki yahoze ifite imbwa nyinshi zo mu gasozi zo muri Afurika. <ref>http://www.apncb.be/archives/publications/fol63694/1962-contribution-la-connaissance-des-lycaons-au-parc-national-de-la-kagera</ref> Igihe kimwe, yari izwi ku izina rya 'Parc aux Lycaons' kandi imbwa zo mu gasozi zari nyinshi cyane, ku buryo leta y'Ububiligi yabonaga ko ari udukoko. Icyakora, icyorezo cyindwara cyarazigabanyije kandi imbwa za nyuma zo mu gasozi zagaragaye mu 1984. <ref name="Vande">Vande weghe, Jean Pierre: ''Akagera: Land of water, grass and fire'' / Jean Pierre Vande weghe. With collaboration of Thérèse Abandibakobwa, José Kalpers a.o. Photography by Philippe Dejace. Translated by Alicia L. Spruijt-Ray. - Brussels: World Wildlife Fund for Nature, 1990</ref>

Mu 1957, inkwavu z'umukara zatangijwe muri Tanzaniya. Mu myaka ya za 70, inkwavu zirabura zirenga 50 zabaga muri savannah-ubuturo bwa parike. Kubera [[Guhiga|guhiga bukware]], abaturage baragabanutse mu myaka icumi yakurikiyeho, kandi iheruka kwemezwa ni mu 2007. <ref name="TheGuardian2017">{{Cite web}}</ref> Mu 1986, Masai giraffes yatangijwe muri Kenya. Umubare wazo wiyongereye kugera aho zirenga 80 mu myaka yashize. Ahagana mu 1990, Akagera kari kazwiho kuba gafite intare hagati ya 250 na 300. <ref name="Vande2">Vande weghe, Jean Pierre: ''Akagera: Land of water, grass and fire'' / Jean Pierre Vande weghe. With collaboration of Thérèse Abandibakobwa, José Kalpers a.o. Photography by Philippe Dejace. Translated by Alicia L. Spruijt-Ray. - Brussels: World Wildlife Fund for Nature, 1990</ref> Mu myaka yakurikiye intambara y'abenegihugu yo mu Rwanda, abaturage bose bishwe n'abahinzi basubiye mu Rwanda nyuma y'intambara maze batura muri parike.

Mu 2009, [[Ikigo gishinzwe iterambere mu Rwanda|Ikigo gishinzwe iterambere ry’u Rwanda]] (RDB) hamwe n’umuyoboro [[Umuyoboro wa Parike nyafurika|nyafurika]] wa [[Umuyoboro wa Parike nyafurika|Afurika]] bagiranye amasezerano y’imyaka 20 ishobora kongerwa ku buyobozi bukuru bwa Akagera. Isosiyete icunga Akagera yashinzwe mu mwaka wa 2010 nk'urwego rushinzwe imiyoborere ya Parike ya Akagera. Mu myaka 5 yakurikiyeho miliyoni 10 z'amadorali yakoreshejwe mu gace ka parike y'igihugu, ku nkunga y'amafaranga yatanzwe na Howard Buffett Foundation. Icyari kigamijwe kwari ukongera umutekano wa parike y’igihugu no kongera kubyara amoko yazimye. Ingamba z’umutekano zafashwe zirimo: kubaka uruzitiro rw’iburengerazuba rufite ibiro metero 120<ref name="TheGuardian20172">{{Cite web}}</ref>, kohereza kajugujugu yo kugenzura ikirere, amahugurwa y’itsinda ry’inzobere mu gukurikirana no kurinda inkwavu n’ishami rishinzwe kurwanya inyamanswa. 

Muri Nyakanga 2015, [[intare]] zirindwi zo muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika y'Epfo]] zamenyekanye kandi zirekurwa muri parike, ziba intare za mbere mu Rwanda mu myaka 15. ''Kandi Beyond'' yatanze intare eshanu zo muri [[Phinda Umukino Wigenga|Phinda Private Game Reserve]] . <ref>{{Cite web}}</ref> na [[Pariki y'inzovu|Tembe Inzovu ya]] [[KwaZulu-Natal]] batanze intare ebyiri zingabo. <ref>{{Cite news}}</ref> Izi mbaraga zasobanuwe na Parike nyafurika ko ari "ingamba zo kubungabunga ibidukikije haba muri parike ndetse n’igihugu" mu rwego rw’umushinga ugamije guhindura ibinyabuabuzima muri Parike ya Akagera. Kuva mu 2015, umubare w'intare wiyongereye kugera ku nyamaswa zigera kuri 40 kandi ukomeza kwiyongera.

Muri Gicurasi 2017, igikorwa cyahurijwe hamwe n’ikigo cy’iterambere ry’u Rwanda na Parike nyafurika cyongeye kugarurwa imvubu 18 [[Inkeri zo mu burasirazuba|z’umukara zo mu Burasirazuba]] ziva muri Afurika yepfo, zari zimaze imyaka 10 zidahari. No kugarurwa kwinkura zirabura nintare, pariki y'igihugu ubu ni urugo rw'inyamaswa  "[[Umukino wa gatanu|eshanu nini]] zo muri Africa ": [[Panthera leo melanochaita|intare]], [[Ingwe yo muri Afurika|ingwe]], [[Inzovu yo muri Afurika|nzovu]], [[Imvubu|Rhinoceros]], n'[[Inyamanswa nyafurika|imbogo .]]

Muri Kamena 2019, Akagera yakiriye izindi [[Inkeri zo mu burasirazuba|nkoko]] 5 [[Inkeri zo mu burasirazuba|z'umukara zo mu burasirazuba]] ziva muri pariki 3 zitandukanye mu bihugu 3 bitandukanye biherereye mu Burayi. Muri pariki harimo inyamaswa zo mu bwoko bwa [[Dvur Kralove zoo|Dvur Kralove zo]] muri Repubulika ya Tchèque, [[Flamingo Land|Flamingo Land yo]] mu Bwongereza na [[Ree Park Safari|Ree Park Safari yo]] muri Danimarike. Uku kwimuka nubwa mbere mubwoko bwayo, ikintu nkiki hagati yuburayi na Afrika ntago kigeze kibaho mbere. Ingabo 2 nizigitsina gore 3 zagejejwe neza muri parike nyuma yurugendo rwamasaha 30. Izi nyamaswa zikomoka ku nkura zakuwe muri Afurika mu gihe cyabakoloni. <ref>{{Cite news}}</ref> <ref>{{Cite news}}</ref>

Umubare munini wiyongereye kuva mu 2010, uva ku nyamaswa 4000 mu 2010 ugera ku 13.500 mu 2018. <ref>https://www.africanparks.org/big-cat-sighting</ref>


'''<big>Ubukerarugendo</big>'''

Kuva Parike nyafurika yatangira gucunga parike ku bufatanye n’ikigo gishinzwe iterambere ry’u Rwanda mu 2010, ubukerarugendo bwiyongereye ku buryo bugaragara. Mu mwaka wa 2010, abantu 8000 basuye parike. Uyu mubare wazamutse ugera ku 44.000 muri 2018. <ref>https://www.africanparks.org/sites/default/files/uploads/resources/2019-07/AFRICAN%20PARKS%20-%202018%20Annual%20Report%20-%20Digital%20-%20English%20-%20Final%20V3.pdf</ref> Uku kwiyongera kwatumye Akagera pariki yibeshaho 80% bityo ntishingire kubaterankunga. <ref>https://www.africanparks.org/sites/default/files/uploads/resources/2019-07/AFRICAN%20PARKS%20-%202018%20Annual%20Report%20-%20Digital%20-%20English%20-%20Final%20V3.pdf</ref>


